title: R-Draw v1.0
description:
Leonardo Da Vinci created all of his notes by mirror writing.

If you think it's impossible... you are wrong! It's as easy as pie and soon you will be able to challenge the genius. Start with writing and sketching by mirror writing! R-Draw will help you. 

Test yourself in 81 different levels. Your time is limited and the sketch is disappearing faster in every turn. Each level brings new challenges.

Warning! Mirror writing is just the beginning.

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.BCG.RDraw
